{"summary":"A WxWidgets based tool for browsing Erlang\n  crashdumps.","description":"<p> </p><p>The Crashdump Viewer is a WxWidgets based tool for browsing Erlang crashdumps.</p> <p>For details about how to get started with the Crashdump Viewer, see the <span class=\"bold_code bc-19\"><a href=\"/erldoc/docs/../apps/observer/crashdump_ug\"><span class=\"code\">User&apos;s Guide</span></a></span>.</p> <p></p>","funcs":" <table class=\"func-table\"><tbody><tr class=\"func-tr\"><td class=\"func-td\"><div class=\"bold_code fun-type\"><span ><span id=\"ghlink-start-0-id73926\" class=\"ghlink\"><a href=\"/erldoc/docs/https://github.com/erlang/otp/edit/maint/lib/observer/doc/src/crashdump.xml#L48\" title=\"Found an issue with the documentation? Fix it by clicking here!\"><span class=\"pencil\"></span></a></span><a class=\"title_link\" name=\"start-0\" href=\"/erldoc/docs/#start-0\">start() -&gt; ok</a></span></div></td><td class=\"func-since-td\"></td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"func-table\"><tbody><tr class=\"func-tr\"><td class=\"func-td\"><div class=\"bold_code fun-type\"><span ><span id=\"ghlink-start-1-id73932\" class=\"ghlink\"><a href=\"/erldoc/docs/https://github.com/erlang/otp/edit/maint/lib/observer/doc/src/crashdump.xml#L48\" title=\"Found an issue with the documentation? Fix it by clicking here!\"><span class=\"pencil\"></span></a></span><a class=\"title_link\" name=\"start-1\" href=\"/erldoc/docs/#start-1\">start(File) -&gt; ok</a></span></div></td><td class=\"func-since-td\"><span class=\"since\">OTP 17.0</span></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"REFBODY rb-5\"><h3 class=\"func-types-title\">Types</h3> <div class=\"REFTYPES rt-4\"><span class=\"bold_code fun-param-type\">File = string()</span><br></div> <div class=\"REFBODY rb-6\">The filename of the crashdump.</div> </div><div class=\"REFBODY rb-7\"><p> </p><p>Starts the Crashdump Viewer GUI and loads the specified crashdump.</p> <p>If <span class=\"code\">File</span> is not specified, a file dialog is opened where the crashdump can be selected.</p> <p></p></div> <table class=\"func-table\"><tbody><tr class=\"func-tr\"><td class=\"func-td\"><div class=\"bold_code fun-type\"><span ><span id=\"ghlink-stop-0-id73975\" class=\"ghlink\"><a href=\"/erldoc/docs/https://github.com/erlang/otp/edit/maint/lib/observer/doc/src/crashdump.xml#L64\" title=\"Found an issue with the documentation? Fix it by clicking here!\"><span class=\"pencil\"></span></a></span><a class=\"title_link\" name=\"stop-0\" href=\"/erldoc/docs/#stop-0\">stop() -&gt; ok</a></span></div></td><td class=\"func-since-td\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"REFBODY rb-7\"><p> </p><p>Terminates the Crashdump Viewer and closes all GUI windows.</p> <p></p></div> "}